<kml>

<concept name=Be-Activated>
<superconcept name=Be-Accessible>

<hr>
<h3>Component Semantics:</h3>
<component tag=Be-Activated>
  <definition>object is activated and is free to participate in various actions
  </definition>
  <requiredslot name=object>
    <restriction>a Entity</restriction>
  </requiredslot>
  <wnsynsets><adj>activated#3
  </adj></wnsynsets>
  <wnsynsets><adj>active#13, on#1
  </adj></wnsynsets>
</component>

<musing>
Be-Activated is a state where the <slot>object</slot> is activated and as
a result, is free to participate in various actions. <conceptref name=Activate> 
puts the object into this state and <conceptref name=Deactivate> takes it out.
</musing>

</kml>


